data.description: *** Assumption is availible with VA loan at 3.5%*** Exquisite 4 bed/3 bath Highland home in the gated community of Stonewall Estates. Kitchen offers rich 42" Espresso cabinetry, granite counters, center island, gas cooking, and built-in SS appliances. Enjoy meals in the formal dining room, or in the breakfast room for a more casual experience. Spacious, open living area with a cozy floor to ceiling limestone fireplace and exterior access to the upper balcony. Primary retreat features sitting area with views of the greenbelt, balcony access, ensuite with double vanity, tile shower + garden tub. Two generously sized secondary bedrooms on the main level with shared bathroom. Lower level of the home provides great entertainment area with large Gameroom, media room, and additional bedroom. Walk-out access to the private backyard, covered patio + open patio area. Convenient to local restaurants, shopping, La Cantera, and Six Flags.
